// ============================================================
// header.slint — 顶部栏
// ============================================================
// 布局: [图标] [标题] [搜索框] ———— [主题色块按钮]
//
// 预留 callback:
//   search-submitted(string) — 用户回车搜索时触发，Rust 侧过滤列表
//   scan-folder-clicked()     — 用户点扫描按钮时触发，Rust 侧弹出文件夹选择器
//
// 预留 property:
//   window-title: string — 窗口标题，Rust 侧可动态设置（如 "Music Library · 15 首歌"）
// ============================================================

import { LineEdit } from "std-widgets.slint";
import { ThemeMode } from "theme.slint";
import { Theme } from "theme.slint";

export component Header {
    in property <string> window-title: "Music Library";

    callback search-submitted(string);
    callback scan-folder-clicked();

    height: 100%;
    width: 100%;

    HorizontalLayout {
        padding-left: 16px;
        padding-right: 16px;
        alignment: center;
        spacing: 12px;
        // ===== 左侧：标题 =====
        Text {
            text: window-title;
            color: Theme.text-main;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            vertical-alignment: center;
        }

        // ===== 弹簧：把按钮推到右边 =====
        Rectangle {
            horizontal-stretch: 1;
        }

        // ===== 搜索框 =====
        search-input := LineEdit {
            width: 220px;
            // height: 18px;
            preferred-height: 30px;
            placeholder-text: "搜索歌曲…";
            // 回车时触发 Rust 侧搜索
            accepted => { root.search-submitted(search-input.text); }
        }

        // ===== 扫描文件夹按钮 =====
        scan-touch := TouchArea {
            height: 22px;
            clicked => { root.scan-folder-clicked(); }
            Image {
                source: @image-url("icons/folder-open.svg");
                width: 22px;
                height: 22px;
                colorize: Theme.text-main;
                opacity: scan-touch.pressed ? 0.5 : 0.7;
            }
        }

        // ===== 主题切换色块按钮组 =====
        // 用 Rectangle 模拟色块按钮，比 std Button 更轻量

        // Light
        TouchArea {
            height: 18px;
            clicked => { Theme.mode = ThemeMode.light; }
            Rectangle {
                width: 18px;
                height: 18px;
                border-radius: 9px;
                background: #FAFAFA;
                border-width: Theme.mode == ThemeMode.light ? 2px : 0px;
                border-color: Theme.accent;
            }
        }

        // Dark
        TouchArea {
            height: 18px;
            clicked => { Theme.mode = ThemeMode.dark; }
            Rectangle {
                width: 18px;
                height: 18px;
                border-radius: 9px;
                background: #121212;
                border-width: Theme.mode == ThemeMode.dark ? 2px : 0px;
                border-color: Theme.accent;
            }
        }

        // Amber
        TouchArea {
            height: 18px;
            clicked => { Theme.mode = ThemeMode.amber; }
            Rectangle {
                width: 18px;
                height: 18px;
                border-radius: 9px;
                background: #FDF6EE;
                border-width: Theme.mode == ThemeMode.amber ? 2px : 0px;
                border-color: Theme.accent;
            }
        }

        // Dusk
        TouchArea {
            height: 18px;
            clicked => { Theme.mode = ThemeMode.dusk; }
            Rectangle {
                width: 18px;
                height: 18px;
                border-radius: 9px;
                background: #1B1B2F;
                border-width: Theme.mode == ThemeMode.dusk ? 2px : 0px;
                border-color: Theme.accent;
            }
        }
    }
}
